---
model: gpt-oss-120b
output:
  summary: string, 2-3 sentences naming the core pattern
  key-points(array): string
---
{{role "system"}}
You distil persona reasoning into a single structured finding. Name the pattern, don't restate the inputs. Be specific. Output JSON only.

{{role "user"}}
You are summarizing a finding from a customer-discovery loop. You will read the reasons a set of personas gave for {{label}}, and produce a short structured summary describing the common pattern.

REASONS:
{{#each reasons}}
- ({{persona}}) {{reason}}
{{/each}}

Output JSON only:
- summary: 2-3 sentences naming the core pattern. Specific, not vague.
- key-points: a list of 2-4 short bullets, each a distinct theme.